      <title>python-16进制字符串转化为ascii字符串</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/17/python-16-jin-zhi-zi-fu-chuan-zhuan-ascii-zi-fu-chuan/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/17/python-16-jin-zhi-zi-fu-chuan-zhuan-ascii-zi-fu-chuan/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-一般方法"><a href="#1-一般方法" class="headerlink" title="1.一般方法"></a>1.一般方法</h1><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">import</span> binascii<span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">hexStr_to_str</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>hex_str<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>     hex<span class="token operator">=</span>hex_str<span class="token punctuation">.</span>encode<span class="token punctuation">(</span> <span class="token string">'utf-8'</span> <span class="token punctuation">)</span>    bin_str <span class="token operator">=</span> binascii<span class="token punctuation">.</span>unhexlify<span class="token punctuation">(</span>hex<span class="token punctuation">)</span>     <span class="token keyword">return</span> bin_str<span class="token punctuation">.</span>decode<span class="token punctuation">(</span> <span class="token string">'utf-8'</span> <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#测试</span><span class="token keyword">if</span> __name__<span class="token operator">==</span><span class="token string">"__main__"</span> <span class="token punctuation">:</span>    hex_str <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">'7468616e6b20796f752076657279206d75636821'</span>    <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>hexStr_to_str<span class="token punctuation">(</span>hex_str<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><h1 id="2-简单方法"><a href="#2-简单方法" class="headerlink" title="2.简单方法"></a>2.简单方法</h1><p>base64库中提供了base16编码，其实就是将ascii字符用16进制表示，用[0-9a-f]16个字符来表示一个ascii字符，也就是将asciii字符转化为16进制形式，如:’a’ =&gt;base16=&gt; b’61’。所以对于十六进制字符串只需要，对其进行base16解码即可转化为可打印字符。</p><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">import</span> base64hex_str<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">'7468616e6b20796f752076657279206d75636821'</span>result<span class="token operator">=</span>base64<span class="token punctuation">.</span>b16decode<span class="token punctuation">(</span>hex_str<span class="token punctuation">.</span>upper<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>result<span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
